{"uid":"f174989502ac1b13","name":"test_remote_sql_flags_survive_real_bash_tokenization","fullName":"tests.tasks.test_tasks_ssh_utils.TestRemoteSnapshotCmd#test_remote_sql_flags_survive_real_bash_tokenization","historyId":"e45cf59e1a758d706541478d1d63c01b","time":{"start":1781379627187,"stop":1781379627190,"duration":3},"description":"Regression for 527623d62: ``remote_snapshot_cmd`` used to splice\n``flags`` with ``' '.join``, so a flag value containing spaces or\nsingle-quotes (typical SQL) was re-tokenized by the remote bash\ninto several argv entries and ``dinary.tools.sql`` received a\ntruncated ``--query``.\n\nVerify the fix end-to-end: feed the generated suffix to an actual\n``bash`` (the same shell the prod transport uses) and observe the\nargv it would hand to ``python -m dinary.tools.sql``.\n","descriptionHtml":"<p>Regression for 527623d62: <code>remote_snapshot_cmd</code> used to splice<br />\n<code>flags</code> with <code>' '.join</code>, so a flag value containing spaces or<br />\nsingle-quotes (typical SQL) was re-tokenized by the remote bash<br />\ninto several argv entries and <code>dinary.tools.sql</code> received a<br />\ntruncated <code>--query</code>.</p>\n<p>Verify the fix end-to-end: feed the generated suffix to an actual<br />\n<code>bash</code> (the same shell the prod transport uses) and observe the<br />\nargv it would hand to <code>python -m dinary.tools.sql</code>.</p>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[{"name":"_stub_socket_getfqdn","time":{"start":1781379570798,"stop":1781379570799,"duration":1},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false,"stepsCount":0,"hasContent":false},{"name":"_disable_drain_loop","time":{"start":1781379627186,"stop":1781379627186,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldD